tafsir[30]{c,v,t}:
  32,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim: fii Й—ee kaalfe yewtanooma ka fuЙ—Й—oode Simoore Albaqarah."
  32,2,"Jippagol ndee Alqur'aanaare nde Muhammadu (yo kisiyee) addi, ko jippiniraande e makko, immorde e JeyЙ—o winndere nden."
  32,3,"ЖЃee heeferЙ“e no wi'a: Muhammadu fefindi nde, o baki e Joomi maako. ЖЉum wanaa non woniri! Si ko woni, ko nde goongaare nde sikke alaa e mu'un, jipporiinde ka Joomi maaЙ—a an NulaaЙ—o, fii yo a jertin yimЙ“e, Й“e NulaaЙ—o araano e mun ado maaЙ—a, hulЙ“inoroowo Й“e lepte Alla Й—en. Belajo'o, Й“e feewiray e goonga kan, Й“e jokka, Й“e gollitira ka."
  32,4,"Ko Alla woni taguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, O tagi ko woni hakkunde majji kon e nder balЙ—e jeegoo. Himo hattani tagugol Й—i e nder dumunna Й“urЙ—o fotoowo ma majaango. Refti O toowi O fotondiri ka dow ""Arsi"", no haandiri e mawngu Makko. Alanaa on, onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, gaanin Alla, giЙ—o heftoowo fii mon, maa tefanoowo on ka Joomi mon. E on waajitotaako, rewon Alla taguЙ—o on, hara on rewidaali Mo e goЙ—Й—um goo?"
  32,5,"Alla no fewjana denndaangal fiyakuuji Й—in ka kammuuli e ka leydi, refti Й—i Жґeengira ka Makko, e nder Г±alaande nde emmbere mun woni, duuЙ“i ujunere e ko limoton onon yimЙ“e Й“en aduna."
  32,6,"On fewjoowo fi Й—um Й—on fow, ko AnnduЙ—o ko wirnii e ko feeГ±i, huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e Й—in Й—iЙ—i, FooluЙ—o yoftot e ayЙ“e mun, Mo gooto foolataa, Hinnotoo jeyaaЙ“e Makko gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en."
  32,7,"On labinЙ—o kala huunde nde O tagi. O fuЙ—Й—i tagudi Aadama ndin e loopal, no anndiranooka."
  32,8,"Refti O waЙ—i genyol makko on Й“aawo makko, tagiraaЙ—o e ndihal sortondir-kal, kal o yalti e mun."
  32,9,"Refti O timminiri tagu neЙ—Й—anke on fotndindirgol mo, O wutti e makko Ruuhu Makko on, e jurol Malaa'ikaajo halfinaaЙ—o Й—um on. Refti O waЙ—ani on onon yimЙ“e Й“en, nanЙ—e ko naniron, e giiЙ—e Й—e yi'iron, e Й“erЙ—e Й—e haqqiliron. Kono fanЙ—ii ko yettoton Й—in neemaaji Alla e dow mooЙ—on."
  32,10,"SirkooЙ“e fennuЙ“e ummital Й“en wi': E nee, si men maayii, fii amen mulii ka leydi, men wontii mbul-mbuldi, hara men wuurnitete kesun? Haqqil jaЙ“aa Й—um. Ko woni kamЙ“e on, ko Й“e yedduЙ“e ummital, Й“e gomЙ—inaa Й—um."
  32,11,"An NulaaЙ—o, maakan Й“ee sirkooЙ“e fennuЙ“e ummital: Ko hunnata on wara on, ko Malaa'ikaajo maayde on wakkilaaЙ—o Жґeetitugol pittaali mon. refti ko ka Amen gaa tun, woni ruttorde mon Г‘alnde Darngal, fii hasbeede yoЙ“itee."
  32,12,"Aray nde bomЙ“e Й“en hoynoytee Г‘alnde Darangal, Й“e ugginira ko'e maЙ“Й“e sabu ko Й“e yeddirnoo ummital kon, Й“e so'a jaasere, Й“e wi': ""Joomi amen, men yi'ii non ko men fennaynoo kon e ummital, men nanii goonga ka NulaaЙ“e Й“en ardunoo e mun kan immorde ka MaaЙ—a, Men torike ma ruttu men ka nguurdam aduna, men golla golle moЖґЖґe, welayЙ—e Ma. Menen men yananaama non hannde, fii ummital e goonga ka NulaaЙ“e Й“en addunoo kan"". Sinno a tinuno bomЙ“e Й“en o on fiyaaku, a tinayno ko mawni."
  32,13,"Sinno Men muuyuno okkugol kala wonkii peewal makki, Men newinaynayno ki Й—um. Ko woni tun, Hikma An on e nunЙ—al an ngal waЙ—Й—inii konngol immorde e An, hebbinirgol Jahannama on Г‘alnde Darngal, yoora k'o'e en, yedduЙ“e Й“en ka jinna e ka yimЙ“e, tawde Й“e suЙ“ike laawol yeddugol e majjere ngol, Й“e acci laawol gomЙ—inal e peewal ngol."
  32,14,"ЖЃe felilorte wi'aneede Г‘alnde Darnnal: ""MeeЙ—iree lepte Й—en, sabu welsindagol mon ka nguurndam aduna, hawrugol e Alla Г‘alnde Darngal, fii hasbu-gol on. Menen kadi Men accii mon ka lepte, Men tefaa ko sa'otoЙ—on e majje. MeeЙ—iree lepte Yiite ngen luttaynge, nge taЖґondirtaa, sabu ko huuwaynoЙ—on kon e geddi ka aduna."
  32,15,"Anndee ko gomЙ—inta Aayeeje Amen jippinaaЙ—e e NulaaЙ—o Amen on, ko Й“en Й“e tawata si Й“e waajoraama Й—en, Й“e suuyiray sujjangol Alla, Й“e subbunhinora yettugol Mo, kamЙ“e Й“e townitantaako rewugol Alla, maa sujjangol Mo."
  32,16,"Becce maЙ“Й“e Й—en hino woЙ—Й—itora danЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й—aanagol, Й“e aciita Й—e Й“e fewta e Alla, Й“e noddira ka julde maЙ“Й“e e ko wonah juulde, kulol lepte Makko Й—en e tama'u yurmeende Makko nden. E senngo goo, hiЙ“e tottira jawle Й—e Men yeЙ—i Й“e Й—en, e fii Alla."
  32,17,"Wonkii woo anndaa ko Alla marani Й“e e ko wallinta Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Й—um ko njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e immorde e Makko, e kon ko Й“e gollaynoo aduna, immorde e golle moЖґЖґe. Ko Alla tun yeЙ—ata ndin njoЙ“di mawndi."
  32,18,"Kala on laatiiЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla, golliri yamaruyeeji Makko, o woЙ—Й—itii haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko, o wa'ataa wa on yaltuЙ—o e Й—oftaare Alla. ЖЃen Й—iЙ—o fotataa e njoЙ“di yeeso Alla."
  32,19,"Si ko Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla, Й“e golli golle moЖґЖґe, njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndi Й“e maranaa ndin, ko Aljannaani Й—i Й“e Г±iiЙ“ata e mun, Й—i Alla teddinirta Й“e. ЖЉum ko njoЙ“di ko Й“e gollaynoo golle moЖґЖґe kon aduna kon."
  32,20,"Si tawnii non ko Й“en yaltirЙ“e e Й—oftaare Alla nden yeddugol faggitoo geddi, haray femporde Й“en Й—on nden Г‘alnde Darngal, ko ka Yiite. Ko Й“e luttooЙ“e e nder magge poomaa. Tuma kala nde Й“e faalaa yaltugol e magge, Й“e ruttitee e magge, Й“e deЖґЖґiniree wi'aneede: ""MeeЙ—ee lepte Yiite nge fennaynoЙ—on ngen aduna, fewndo NulaaЙ“e mon Й“en hulЙ“iniraynoo on nge""."
  32,21,"Ma Men meeЙ—inir Й“ee heeferЙ“e fennooЙ“e yaltuЙ“e e Й—oftaare Joomi maЙ“Й“e, saЙ—teende e jarrabuyee aduna, ado lepte mawЙ—e Й—e Й“e hebilanaa Й—en laakara, si Й“e tuubaali, belajo'o, Й“e yiltoto e Й—oftagol Joomi maaЙ“e."
  32,22,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГ±ude wano waajoraaЙ—o Aayeeje Alla Й—en, o salii waajitorde Й—e, o Й—uurnii Й—e o itti yiila e majje. Pellet, Menen, ko Men yoftotooЙ“e e bomЙ“e faggitotooЙ“e keeferaaru e geddi Й“en, Й—uurnotooЙ“e e Aayeeje Alla Й—en."
  32,23,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa Tawreetaare nden. Wata an NulaaЙ—o, a wonu e sikke e fii hawroygol e Muusaa jemma royreede e Жґawneede. Men waЙ—i Deftere jippinaande e Muusaa nden, fewnaynde Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iila Й“en."
  32,24,"Men waЙ—i e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, ardiiЙ“e ko yimЙ“e Й“en Г±emtina, Й“e Й—owiraЙ“e e goonga, tuma nde Й“e muГ±Г±inoo e Й—oftagol yamaruyeeji Alla, e woЙ—iitagol haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko e lorra ko Й“e hawrata e noddangol diina kan, Й“e woni goonginirЙ“e pellital, Aayeeje Alla jippinaaЙ—e e NulaaЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on."
  32,25,"Pellet, Joomi maa an NulaaЙ—o, ko Kanko senndoyta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Г‘alnde Darangal, e kon ko Й“e lurraynoo e fii mun aduna. O Й“anngina goonguЙ—o e meerente, O yoЙ“ita kala e ko hanndi kon."
  32,26,"E Й“ee wumu haa ka tawata feeГ±anaali Й“e no foti e ko Men halki e mofte adinooЙ“e? KamЙ“e hiЙ“e jinnda e koЙ—oole Й—i Й“en hoЙ—unoo e mun e Й“e halkeede, kono Й“e waajitoraali fiyaaku Й“en on. Pellet, no e ngol peЖґЖґol Й—en mofte halkiranooЙ“e sabu keeferaaku e geddi mun, tasakuyee dallinorЙ—o goongugol kon ko NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e addani Й“e immorde ka Alla. E Й“ee fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Alla kan nanataa, Й“e jaЙ“a Й“e waajitora?"
  32,27,"E Й“ee fennuЙ“e ummital yi'ataa, wonnde Men nuliray ndiyam toЙ“o ngon ka leydi hokkundi, Men yaltinira Й—am remuru, ngu gelooЙ—i e na'i e be'i maЙ“Й“e Г±aamata e mun, e kamЙ“e tigirigi? E Й“e yi'ataa Й—um, Й“e anndaa wonnde fuЙ—inЙ—o leydi hokkundi ndin, ko hattanЙ—o wuurnitugol maayЙ“e?"
  32,28,"ЖЃee fennuЙ“e ummital no wi'ira hawjanjangol lepte Й—en : ""Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Г±aawoore nde aaЖґiЙ—on, wonnde nde senndoyay hakkunde men Г‘alnde Darngal, men fewra Yiita, sutoron Aljanna?"""
  32,29,"Maakan Й“e an NulaaЙ—o: ""Nden fodoore, ko Г‘alnde Darngal: Г±alaande senndindirgol hakkunde jeyaaЙ“e Й“en. Nden Г±alnde, Й“en yeddunooЙ“e Alla Й“en aduna, Й“e nafitoroytaa ko Й“en gomЙ—inoyta tuma Й“e yi'ata Darngal, wanaa kadi Й“e nennantee-Й“e, sakko Й“e tuubana Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ruttoo e Makko""."
  32,30,"An NulaaЙ—o, Й—uurnorЙ“e ko Й“e haЙ“Й“itii kon e majjere, haЙ“Й“ito-Й—aa ko yanata e maЙ“Й“e kon, tawde kamЙ“e kan, ko Й“e haЙ“Й“itiiЙ“e lepte Й—e hebilanaa Й—en."
